1. *Hvala* ti puno! (Thank you very much!)
2. Nisam znao da ću tako dobro proći, *hvala* ti! (I didn't know I was going to do so well, thank you!)
3. *Hvala* ti na izdvojenom vremenu. (Thanks for taking the time.)
4. *Hvala* ti na divnoj večeri. (Thank you for the wonderful evening.)
5. Zbogom, *hvala*. (Goodbye, thank you.)